sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant System
    participant MetadataEngine
    participant ExcelAdapter
    participant HeaderMapper
    participant SchemaValidator
    participant Contract
    participant Normalizer
    participant WarehouseBuilder
    participant BusinessEngine
    participant ValidationEngine
    participant PresentationEngine
    participant ExportEngine
    participant Dashboard

    User->>System: Upload Master File
    System->>MetadataEngine: Extract metadata
    MetadataEngine-->>System: Metadata
    System->>ExcelAdapter: Load workbook
    ExcelAdapter-->>System: Raw rows
    System->>HeaderMapper: Map headers
    HeaderMapper-->>System: Normalized headers
    System->>SchemaValidator: Validate schema
    SchemaValidator-->>System: Validation report
    System->>Contract: Enforce data contract
    Contract-->>System: Contract-conformant rows
    System->>Normalizer: Normalize values
    Normalizer-->>System: Canonical rows
    System->>WarehouseBuilder: Store snapshot
    WarehouseBuilder-->>System: Snapshot path
    System->>BusinessEngine: Run business calculations
    BusinessEngine-->>System: Derived artifacts
    System->>ValidationEngine: Run validations
    ValidationEngine-->>System: Validation report
    System->>PresentationEngine: Prepare presentation datasets
    PresentationEngine-->>System: Presentation datasets
    System->>ExportEngine: Export files/APIs
    ExportEngine-->>System: Export results
    System->>Dashboard: Update dashboards
    Dashboard-->>User: Visualizations
